This paper is about deep learning using spiking neural networks, which falls under the category of neural networks and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses training methods and optimization techniques, which are common topics in the sub-categories of machine learning such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions applications in computer vision (cs.CV) and real-time/mobile systems (cs.SY), which are also relevant sub-categories.
